# UgaTaima Forest Map (biome: forest)
#
# Symbols resolve via assets/tiles.yaml for the "forest" biome. The map viewer
# shows the authoritative, data-driven legend with tile/monster previews.
# Tiles used here:
# . = grass floor   % = thicket   T = tree   A = ancient tree   R = moss rock
# C = clearing      P = fern patch   F = firefly swarm   M = fairy ring
# S = forest stream W = water         Q = deep water       D = door
# - = low wall      = = high wall     + = start
# Highlands portal: K = highland rock outcrop post (flanks the gate). The center
#   @ is the spriteless portal_gate_highlands NPC; its ground_tile paints the
#   portal-stream water under it. Interact opens "travel to the highlands?".
# Monster spawns: b=bear f=forest orc g=goblin l=troll n=bandit p=pixie
#                 t=treant w=wolf
# @ = NPC / special-tile placeholder (bound by >[npc:...] / >[stile:...] at line end)

